quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,89,"Nde deftere ari e ma…ď…ďe iwde e Alla, ende nuun…óina ko …ďe njogii ado …óuum …ďe ngonndoo ko wallitoraade …óum dow …ďeen yeddu…ďe nde ko …ďe nganndi ko ari he ma…ď…ďe …ďe njeddi …óum, yo ku…ódi Alla won he heefer…ďe."
  2,90,"Bone wonii he ko…ďe coodiri ko'e ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe njeddi -e too√Īe- ko Alla jippini , Alla jippinta …ďural Makko dow mbo O welaa e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďe kaandii e tikkere mawnde, heefer…ďe …ďee na ke…ďa lette bon…óe."
  2,91,"Si …ďe mbi'aama ngoong…óinee ko Alla jippini koo …ďe mbi'a min ngoong…óinii ko jippinaa he amen …ďe njedda ko wonaa …óuum te ko …óuum woni goonga nuun…óin…óo ko …ďe njogii, wi' …ďe ko wa…ói o…óon mbarannoo (mbaratnoo) annabaa…ďe Alla …ďee so tawno o…óon ngoong…óini."
  2,92,"Nde Muusaa addani on la…ď…ďinale njogiti-…óon gool oo …ďaawo makko onon ko on too√Īoo…ďe."
  2,93,"Min …ďamii he mon fodoore min …ďamti dow mon haayre Tuur ∆īettiree ko min ngaddani on koo he semmbe nanee, …ďe mbi'i min nanii min ngoopi , …ďer…óe mum en …óe keewi dak rewde gool oo he keefeeru ma…ď…ďe, wiy bone wonii he ko goong…óingol mon yamiri on so tawno o…óon ngoong…óini."